contentrichtext.text: '''QD''' may refer to: * [[Air Class Líneas Aéreas]] IATA airline designator * [[Quantic Dream]] * [[Quantum dot]] * ''[[quaque die]]'', a Latin phrase meaning "every day" * [[Quarter-deck]], a part of a ship * [[Queen Dowager]] * [[Questioned document examination|Questioned Documents]], the field of forensics that deals with the scientific examination of documents * [[Nokia N-Gage QD]] * [[Quill and Dagger]], a Senior Honor Society at Cornell University * [[ATCvet code QD]] ''Dermatologicals'', a section of the Anatomical Therapeutic Chemical Classification System for veterinary medicinal products {{disambig}}
